title: Ravel Introduction et Allegro/Debussy Danse Sacre et Profane
description: Very early 10" VINYL LP RECORD. Ravel and Debussy played by The Hollywood String Quartet with string ensemble conducted by Felix Slatkin. Ann Mason Stockton, Harp; Arthur Gleghorn, Flute; Mitchell Lurie, Clarinet; in Ravel - Introduction et Allegro and Claude Debussy Danses Sacree et Profane.
